description:
Effortlessly transfer, backup, and manage your iPhone data with EaseUS MobiMover

Multi-directional Transfer on iPhone, Android, PC and Mac

Browse and access files on your iPhone, and easily transfer individual files or a batch of data between your iPhone and your computer. Especially when you want to transfer photos from your computer to your iPhone for sharing on Facebook, Twitter or Instagram or other purposes.

Delete files in bulk on your iPhone to optimize storage space. Easily free up storage by removing multiple files at once. You can also uninstall unwanted apps with one-click.

Devices Supported
- Android: Samsung, Google, and Moto smartphones and tablets running Android 5.0 and above.
- All models of iPhone that can run iOS 18 Beta/17/16/15/14/13/11/10, iOS 9 and former; iPad: All models of iPad Air (4th Gen), iPad mini, iPad Pro and iPad that can run iPadOS 18 Beta/17/16/15/14/13.
